{"tid":2192423,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【網民為阿嬌出頭】鍾欣潼傷頭縫針留院 前夫賴弘國孖美女做運動","createTime":"2020-09-07T06:05:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T15:00:13.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ad9a44f9cb558f511e900dbd4e674ad6f8e76bdb","tid":2192423,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T06:05:43.000Z","msg":"鍾欣潼（阿嬌）近日正在廈門趕拍網絡電影，今日凌晨卻在酒店發生意外，頭部受傷入院，令粉絲擔心。據知，阿嬌在醫院經過初步檢查後，已經縫針，今早跟家人和公司報平安，但仍需接受進一步檢查。而身在佛山的前夫賴弘國，今早巧合地在微博貼出跟美女做運動照片，有網民質問他為何不去關心前妻傷勢。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200907/IDFGXULZNVHKLMYWT6WYGR3KSY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200907%2FIDFGXULZNVHKLMYWT6WYGR3KSY%2F&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNpzKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=bd7f7540\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200907%2FIDFGXULZNVHKLMYWT6WYGR3KSY%2F&h=a0a48159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200907/IDFGXULZNVHKLMYWT6WYGR3KSY/</a>"},{"pid":"cf61a26d2fc9ede492465f53a3dc4d08d9ed6ebd","tid":2192423,"uid":51932,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T06:15:20.000Z","msg":"俾佢嫌棄，仲要去關心個八婆，好撚得閒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d09d15c06061d42b055fc86972394dff3828b28","tid":2192423,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf61a26d2fc9ede492465f53a3dc4d08d9ed6ebd","tid":2192423,"uid":51932,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T06:15:20.000Z","msg":"俾佢嫌棄，仲要去關心個八婆，好撚得閒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T06:30:19.000Z","msg":"咪就係"},{"pid":"122b2c3781db980f06d79a1e79b56c28d8d142a8","tid":2192423,"uid":4826,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cf61a26d2fc9ede492465f53a3dc4d08d9ed6ebd","tid":2192423,"uid":51932,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"re